Vela brand assets are Apache-2.0 alongside the rest of the repository.

Mark, wordmark, favicon, and rete motif are derived from the public astrolabe
vocabulary — rings, alidade, engraved ticks, a signal star. No third-party
trademarks are incorporated.

The single signal-blue accent (#3B5BDB) is part of the brand and should only be
used to mark live state in interfaces that use the Vela identity. See
docs/BRAND.md for the full canon.
